'''NGC 4845'''，或稱為'''NGC 4910'''，是一個距離地球約4700萬光年的[[螺旋星系|螺旋星系]]，在天球上位於[[室女座|室女座]]。該星系由[[威廉·赫歇爾|威廉·赫歇爾]]發現於1786年<ref>{{cite web|url=http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc48.htm#4845|title=NGC Objects: NGC 4800-4849|publisher=Courtney Seligman|accessdate=May 13, 2013|archive-date=2019-02-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190220072201/http://cseligman.com/text/atlas/ngc48.htm#4845|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

NGC 4845的中心有個質量為300,000[[太陽質量|<math>\begin{smallmatrix}M_\odot\end{smallmatrix}</math>]]的[[超大質量黑洞|超大質量黑洞]]。2013年，[[歐洲太空總署|歐洲太空總署]]的[[国际伽玛射线天体物理实验室|国际伽玛射线天体物理实验室]]（INTEGRAL）觀測到了該黑洞可能正在吞噬周圍可能是[[棕矮星|棕矮星]]等低質量天體時發射出的X射線閃焰<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.nationalpost.com/2013/04/04/astronomers-watch-as-supermassive-black-hole-wakes-up-swallows-planet-whole/|title=Astronomers watch as supermassive black hole ‘wakes up,’ swallows planet whole|publisher=National Post|date=April 4, 2013|accessdate=May 13, 2013|archive-date=2014-12-31|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141231210928/http://news.nationalpost.com/2013/04/04/astronomers-watch-as-supermassive-black-hole-wakes-up-swallows-planet-whole/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.geekosystem.com/ngc-4845-black-hole-eats-planet/|title=Watch a Black Hole Feed on Its Planet-Sized Prey|author=Jeff LaSala|publisher=Geekosystem|date=April 3, 2013|accessdate=May 13, 2013|archive-date=2014-01-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140128021143/http://www.geekosystem.com/ngc-4845-black-hole-eats-planet/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Supermassive and super-hungry|url=http://www.spacetelescope.org/images/potw1601a/|accessdate=4 January 2016|archive-date=2016-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160315162521/http://www.spacetelescope.org/images/potw1601a/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

